contentrichtext.text: '''Cocos''' may refer to: * [[Cocos (genus)|Cocos ''(genus)'']], a plant genus with the coconut as its only accepted species * [[Cocos Lagoon]], south of Guam * [[Cocos (Keeling) Islands]] * [[Cocos Malays]], an ethnic group inhabiting the [[Cocos (Keeling) Islands]] * [[Cocos Plate]], a tectonic plate beneath the Pacific Ocean * [[Battle of Cocos]], 1914 naval battle near the Cocos (Keeling) Islands * [[Orang Cocos]], an ethnic group in Malaysia descended from Cocos Malay immigrants ==See also== * [[Coco (disambiguation)]] * [[Coconut (disambiguation)]] * [[Cocos Island (disambiguation)]] {{Disambig}}
